ody></table><h1>Cambios en la configuraci&oacute;n</h1><p>PR config Staging: &lt;LINK A PR&gt;</p><p>PR config Producci&oacute;n: &lt;LINK A PR&gt;</p><h1>Migraciones a ejecutar</h1><p>&lt;Listado de todas las migraciones que se deben ejecutar&gt;</p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"8ef4b99d-c1aa-4437-a074-f0056b21cf68\"><ac:parameter ac:name=\"language\">sql</ac:parameter><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[CREATE TABLA ...]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro><h1>Datos a insertar</h1><h2><span style=\"color: rgb(151,160,175);\">Commerce Service:</span></h2><p>CREACION DEL SERVICIO:</p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"5c6a07b8-4340-4bcc-a74a-2ab544d6034c\"><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[INSERT INTO services(name)VALUE('pix');]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro><p>CREACION DE LA ROLE_CATEGORY:</p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"2de04416-5637-4a96-bae0-01588633a363\"><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[INSERT INTO role_categories(name, description)VALUE('pix', 'PIX');]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro><p>CREACION DEL ROLE CAJERO PIX:</p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"9a6021bc-3fd6-48f2-98ed-e71febe5dfe0\"><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[INSERT INTO roles(name, description, role_category_id)\nVALUES\n  ('pix_cashier', 'Cajero PIX', ->ID DEL ROLE_CATEGORY PIX<-),\n  ('pix_supervisor', 'Supervisor PIX', ->ID DEL ROLE_CATEGORY PIX<-);]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro><p>CREACION DE PERMISSIONS:</p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"daa9da17-b8d1-4678-b211-d31a93ddb92c\"><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[INSERT INTO permissions(name, description)\nVALUES\n\t('services_pix', 'Servicio PIX'),\n\t('services_pix__cashier_basic_management', 'Servicio PIX -> Permisos de Cajero'),\n\t('services_pix__branch_management', 'Servicio PIX -> Permisos de Gestion De Sucursal'),\n\t('services_pix__all_branches_management', 'Servicio PIX -> Permisos de Gestión de Comercio');]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro><p>CREACION DE ROLE_PERMISSIONS:</p><ac:structured-macro ac:name=\"code\" ac:schema-version=\"1\" ac:macro-id=\"b413a144-4f9d-42a3-9764-d68ecb891a24\"><ac:plain-text-body><![CDATA[INSERT INTO permission_roles\n\t(permission_id, role_id)\nVALUES\n\t(-> services_pix permission_id <-, -> superadmin role_id <-),\n\t(-> services_pix permission_id <-, -> pix_cashier role_id <-),\n\t(-> services_pix permission_id <-, -> pix_supervisor role_id <-),\n\t(-> __cashier_basic_management permission_id <-,-> pix_cashier role_id <-),\n\t(-> __all_branches_management permission_id <-,-> super_admin role_id <-),\n\t(-> __branch_management permission_id <-, -> pix_supervisor role_id <-);]]></ac:plain-text-body></ac:structured-macro><h1>Pull requests a develop/master</h1><ul><li><p>&lt;link a pr en github&gt;</p></li></ul><p /><p />","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/2757492739"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":389},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2757492739/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/2757492739/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/2757492739/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/2757492739/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2757492739","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2757492739/Deploy+a+producci+n","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2757492739","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2757492739","tinyui":"/x/AwBcp","collection":"/rest/api/co